Class Route

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMetadataContainer

    public class Route
extends IdBaseNamed
implements IMetadataContainer
    Encapsulates data related to a Route in a TracTrac Event.

    An instance of this class has a unique id and a name. Custom data may be attached to each route instance.

    Use Event.addRoute(java.util.UUID, java.lang.String) to create a new Route.

    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    TracTrac
